{"type":"message","id":"c211d39b","parentId":"844234be","timestamp":"2026-05-01T19:24:50.445Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is asking why I sent a voice memo. Looking at the context, he told me earlier he wants voice memos to be conversational and easy to answer back. He also said earlier \"i want you to send me the link again\" and \"you are just sending http://localhost:8790/questionnaire.html as plain text and im not able to click on it. why is that\" - he was frustrated about plain text links.\n\nBut wait - he also said \"i want it to work like voice mode on chatgpt\" and wanted the voice communication to be through Telephone. And in an earlier message he said \"i want it to work like voice mode on chatgpt. i would want it to be a tool for me and you to communicate.\"\n \nI realize I made a mistake by sending a voice memo to introduce Telephone when he specifically wanted that communication channel to feel conversational and easy to respond to - the voice memo format works against that goal. I should've just sent the clickable link instead.\n","thinkingSignature":"1ecf81e52b2bf01d65f026f4168817d191e6002b260d91c16b0f5c8ed72d0b4c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nMy bad — you're right, I shouldn't have sent a voice memo there. You just asked for a clickable link, not a recording. I overcomplicated it.\n\nHere's the link:\n\n[http://192.168.1.162:8790/telephone.html](http://192.168.1.162:8790/telephone.html)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":87331,"output":281,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87740,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777663480401,"responseId":"064430f92cc1d57c8ce84d8a7958e856"}}
