{"type":"message","id":"d8111708","parentId":"a7b6e6c9","timestamp":"2026-05-01T19:50:22.882Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dfucly2i1mix_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### Message Formatting Rules (Telegram)\n- **ALL links must be clickable:** Use `[text](url)` markdown format, NEVER plain URLs\n  - ✅ Correct: `[Fill out the questionnaire](http://localhost:8790/questionnaire.html)`\n  - ❌ Wrong: `http://localhost:8790/questionnaire.html` or `here's the link: http://...`\n- This applies to EVERY link — local URLs, web links, everything\n\n### Voice Memos (System Voice)\n- **Format:** MP3 — always convert with ffmpeg: `say \"text\" -o /tmp/voice.aiff && ffmpeg -i /tmp/voice.aiff /tmp/voice.mp3 -y`\n- **Voice:** System default — no `-v` flag, no voice specification\n- **Send:** Use message tool with `asVoice: true` and `filePath` pointing to the MP3\n- **Always test first** if unsure whether it worked\n\n### When Bobby Reports a Problem\n- **ALWAYS correct it immediately** when he flags an issue\n- Don't wait, don't explain why it happened — just fix it\n- Then note it so it doesn't happen again\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777665022882}}
{"type":"message","id":"52032f28","parentId":"d8111708","timestamp":"2026-05-01T19:50:30.932Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can edit the right section.\n","thinkingSignature":"e6f546e1f80d56fd889597e382c3b12438a0af6827931b73b074b0d74e5594a3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oj6q6eovlegs_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"### Message Formatting Rules (Telegram)\n- **ALL links must be sent as inline buttons** — NOT markdown, NOT plain URLs\n  - Use `presentation: {\"blocks\": [{\"type\": \"buttons\", \"buttons\": [{\"label\": \"text\", \"url\": \"https://...\", \"style\": \"primary\"}]}]}`\n  - Plain URLs or markdown `[text](url)` will NOT render as clickable links\n  - Always include a short message BEFORE the button (e.g. \"Tap the link:\")\n  - Example:\n    ```\n    message: \"Tap to open\"\n    presentation: {\"blocks\": [{\"type\": \"buttons\", \"buttons\": [{\"label\": \"Open Page\", \"url\": \"https://link\", \"style\": \"primary\"}]}]}\n    ```","oldText":"### Message Formatting Rules (Telegram)\n- **ALL links must be clickable:** Use `[text](url)` markdown format, NEVER plain URLs\n  - ✅ Correct: `[Fill out the questionnaire](http://localhost:8790/questionnaire.html)`\n  - ❌ Wrong: `http://localhost:8790/questionnaire.html` or `here's the link: http://...`\n- This applies to EVERY link — local URLs, web links, everything"}],"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":385,"output":347,"cacheRead":57344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58076,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777665022884,"responseId":"064436ffd4c336950a5621a85255d990"}}
