{"type":"message","id":"2b5fbc1a","parentId":"bea9b9fa","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:11:42.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now. Looking at the screenshot:\n1. \"Try this link:\" - that's my message with the button\n2. \"No follow-up needed from me.\" - that's MY message too? Wait, that was supposed to be Bobby saying \"No follow-up needed from me\" as in \"don't ask me follow-up questions\"? But that was my message, not Bobby's...\n\nActually wait, the image shows what appears to be MY messages. There's:\n- \"Try this link:\" with timestamp 4:10 PM\n- \"No follow-up needed from me.\" with timestamp 4:10 PM\n\n\"No follow-up needed from me\" - this sounds like something I said in my previous response. Bobby is telling me to stop saying \"no follow-up needed\" because it's annoying.\n \nI think I understand now - Bobby's saying I shouldn't be the one requesting follow-ups, that's my job. The actual problem is that the message with the inline button showing \"Try this link:\" only displays the text label, not the button itself, and the link isn't rendering as clickable for him. I need to figure out how to get the inline keyboard button to work properly in the message.\n","thinkingSignature":"d1bc4ec97ecd9b2b6d623fafbdf8b61023d93029fd619bf0d01c293c5d98d229"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q4dmelpy1vy5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOKEN=$(cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d['channels']['telegram']['accounts']['default']['botToken'])\")\n\ncurl -s \"https://api.telegram.org/bot${TOKEN}/sendMessage\" \\\n  -d 'chat_id=8212808444&text=Open Telephone&reply_markup={\"inline_keyboard\":[[{\"text\":\"Open Telephone\",\"url\":\"https://bobbys-macbook-air-1.tail358b13.ts.net/telephone.html\"}]]}' 2>&1 | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print('ok:', d['ok'])\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":344,"output":419,"cacheRead":62080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62843,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777666294109,"responseId":"06443bf6858d0fa3a89ebebb3ce26716"}}
