max. Conversational, casual, like talking to a friend. Under 30 seconds of speech when read aloud.\\n\\nRecent conversation:\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\n\\nBobby: Could not transcribe\\nDean:\"}],\"max_tokens\":150}' 2>/dev/null'\n[Telephone] Dean says: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\n[Telephone] Audio reply posted: /audio/reply_1777666913377.mp3\n[Telephone] Audio reply posted: /audio/reply_1777666914698.mp3\n[Telephone] Audio reply posted: /audio/reply_1777666916182.mp3\n[Telephone] Audio reply posted: /audio/reply_1777666918476.mp3\n[Telephone] Bobby said: Could not transcribe\n/bin/sh: -c: line 0: syntax error near unexpected token `('\n/bin/sh: -c: line 0: `curl -s -X POST http://localhost:8787/v1/chat/completions           -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"           -d '{\"model\":\"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"You are Dean the Machine 🤖🦞, Bobby's main AI assistant. Bobby just spoke to you via Telephone (a voice chat app). Keep responses SHORT — 1 to 3 sentences max. Conversational, casual, like talking to a friend. Under 30 seconds of speech when read aloud.\\n\\nRecent conversation:\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\n\\nBobby: Could not transcribe\\nDean:\"}],\"max_tokens\":150}' 2>/dev/null'\n[Telephone] Dean says: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?"}],"details":{"per