{"type":"message","id":"fc712df9","parentId":"192a3066","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:35:17.558Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The servers are running. Bobby is asking if everything is okay and what I was working on. The heartbeat just fired while I was debugging the Telephone app.\n\nThe Telephone app was working in my test - I sent audio through and got transcription. Let me explain what happened and reassure Bobby.\n\nThe issue is: when Bobby speaks into his iPhone, Safari records audio but Whisper can't transcribe it. My test from Mac terminal worked fine. The problem seems to be with Safari's audio format.\n\nI was in the middle of testing webm format when it got cut off by the heartbeat. Let me tell Bobby what happened and that the servers ARE running.\n","thinkingSignature":"cf5ecd03afb473144326152bb982cd7b0f033e1ae6901104c102e99bcebfb934"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nYeah everything's fine! The servers are running. \n\nI was debugging why **Telephone can't transcribe your voice** — every time you talk, Dean responds \"I'm here Bobby, what's up?\" because the audio isn't making it through properly.\n\n**What I found:**\n- Whisper works fine when I test from Mac terminal\n- The server successfully transcribed \"Hello Dean, this is a test\" sent via curl\n- The problem is Safari on iPhone encodes audio differently than the Mac test files\n\nI was testing the webm format handling when the heartbeat fired. Let me get back to it — the servers are running and the transcription pipeline itself is working. The issue is specifically Safari's audio format from MediaRecorder.\n\nWant me to keep working on it or would you rather use Telephone for voice commands some other way for now? I can also try having you test it from your phone to see if the actual iPhone mic → Safari → server pipeline works differently than my Mac-based tests."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":265,"output":332,"cacheRead":63680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64277,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777667708159,"responseId":"0644417c2d71cd98adc510b1e7c20449"}}
