{"type":"message","id":"cb7ef3fc","parentId":"4bc9211e","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:37:30.275Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to know what I need to fix it. Let me think about this practically.\n\nThe problem: Safari on iPhone sends audio in a format that ffmpeg can't process properly, so Whisper gets an empty/corrupt file.\n\nWhat I need to test: Actually record from iPhone Safari and see what format it produces. I can do this by:\n\n1. Having Bobby open telephone.html on his iPhone\n2. Make a recording\n3. Check the server logs to see what file was received, what format it is, how big it is\n\nFrom my earlier tests, I know:\n- The server receives the audio (file is created)\n- ffmpeg is being called but something fails\n\nThe key diagnostic I need is: what does Safari actually send? I can check the log files to see:\n- File size received\n- What ffmpeg reports about the input format\n\nLet me check the server logs to see what's happening when a real recording comes in.\n\nActually, the real issue might be that I was testing with .aiff files but Safari sends .webm. Let me test that specifically.\n\nLet me just ask Bobby to test it from his phone while I watch the logs.\n","thinkingSignature":"5e4abd4dd5a14d123ee1698231bad16e1b57d5ebea8ce150e2ee4d4e079c4d41"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nJust need **you to test it** from your iPhone while I watch what happens.\n\nHere's what to do:\n\n1. Open this URL in Safari on your iPhone:\n   `https://bobbys-macbook-air-1.tail358b13.ts.net/telephone.html`\n\n2. Tap and hold the mic button — speak for 2-3 seconds (\"Hey Dean, what's my name?\"), then release\n\n3. Tell me what you see on screen\n\nWhile you do that, I'll watch the server logs to see:\n- What format Safari is sending\n- How big the file is\n- Where exactly it fails\n\nThat's all I need — a real iPhone recording going through while I watch the logs. Ready when you are."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":63925,"output":401,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64518,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777667834777,"responseId":"064441fbb0b49823cea96392f7f81df6"}}
