{"type":"message","id":"643132de","parentId":"77cbe9a9","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:45:34.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see there's still an issue - Dean is getting \"Not found\" responses from the AI. The transcript is going through (\"Hello Dean, this is a test\" worked) but when Dean tries to respond, he's getting an error. And the AI reply is coming back as \"I'm here Bobby, say something!\" which is wrong.\n\nThe issue is the AI call is failing. Let me look at the dean.js - it should be calling the gateway on port 18789 with the gateway token. Let me check what the problem is.\n\nActually, looking at the logs:\n- `[Telephone] AI parse error: Unexpected token 'N', \"Not Found\" is not valid JSON Not Found` - This means the AI call returned \"Not Found\" (a 404 response). \n\n\n- `[Telephone] Dean says: I'm here Bobby, say something!` - This is Dean's fallback response when the AI call fails.\n\nThe root cause is that the AI call to the gateway is failing with a 404. The gateway port might be wrong, or the endpoint path is wrong. I've got the gateway token already, so I need to check the dean.js configuration and make sure it's pointing to the right endpoint.\n","thinkingSignature":"236ee51d42d6113e8d64dc160b5e5f75a3c510bfea3e484b419f1d8f5f9bece4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nServers are all running. Link is live — Bobby can test whenever he's ready.\n\nI'm watching the logs — I see Dean is still getting \"Not Found\" errors when trying to generate responses. The transcription is working but the AI call itself is failing. Let me fix that now.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2w05qm4qbb7v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test gateway API call directly to find the right endpoint\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:18789/ \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"import json,sys; print(json.load(sys.stdin)['gateway']['auth']['token'])\")\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"test\"}],\"max_tokens\":10}' 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":469,"output":446,"cacheRead":64832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65747,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777668322212,"responseId":"064443e2e393672b3d4370179c80e044"}}
