{"type":"message","id":"fda32457","parentId":"48906a95","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:48:09.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, qwen3:4b seems to be hanging. Maybe the model is still loading or there's an issue. Let me try a different approach - use the OpenClaw gateway tool for Dean to call AI. But first, let me check if there's a way to get a local AI working.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The core problem isn't the AI - it's the transcription failing. Dean is responding \"I'm here Bobby\" because the AI call is failing (or returning \"Could not transcribe\"), not because the AI itself is broken.\n\nLet me go back to the real issue: **Safari on iPhone isn't sending audio that Whisper can transcribe**. \n\nLet me look at what the server is actually receiving when Bobby records from his phone. I need to debug the actual phone recording.\n\nFor now, let me:\n1. Switch dean.js to use the OpenClaw gateway tool call (via sessions_send to the main session)\n2. Or, just make the phone test easier by having server.js save the raw audio file so I can inspect it\n\nActually, the better approach is:\n1. Have server.js save the raw audio BEFORE attempting transcription, so I can inspect what Safari is actually sending\n2. Then I can see if it's a format issue, a size issue, or something else\n\n\n3. Let me modify server.js to preserve the raw audio file before the transcription pipeline processes it, so I can examine what Safari actually sent.\n","thinkingSignature":"de12dadc0119c05d207e87e7be932315c869ff9e11e6572f033e9fb30552e735"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_99nes3ftmcvf_1","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"tidy-crustacean"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":158,"output":338,"cacheRead":94016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94512,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777668478592,"responseId":"0644447f40b74902c2a25a9e95905e99"}}
