le>Error response</title>\n    </head>\n    <body>\n        <h1>Error response</h1>\n        <p>Error code: 404</p>\n        <p>Message: File not found.</p>\n        <p>Error code explanation: 404 - Nothing matches the given URI.</p>\n    </body>\n</html>\n<!DOCTYPE HTML>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n    <head>\n        <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n        <style type=\"text/css\">\n            :root {\n                color-scheme: light dark;\n            }\n        </style>\n        <title>Error response</title>\n    </head>\n    <body>\n        <h1>Error response</h1>\n        <p>Error code: 501</p>\n        <p>Message: Unsupported method ('POST').</p>\n        <p>Error code explanation: 501 - Server does not support this operation.</p>\n    </body>\n</html>","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777668796941}}
{"type":"message","id":"576505b7","parentId":"ef4e8c62","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:53:21.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Python server is still running (port 8790) and is still serving static files. It doesn't proxy POST requests to 8791. The issue is the Python server is still running on 8790 and it's not proxying. I need to kill it and start the Node proxy.\n\nWait, I tried to kill it with `pkill -f \"59062\"` but it might not have worked. Let me check.\n","thinkingSignature":"9bae4713655864a37a5976cb3bde3ba8d2f3b8f80f6f79a3441777ef7bfd98e3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uznfpjc0ldwx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Python server still running - kill it properly\nlsof -ti:8790 | xargs kill -9 2>/dev/null\nsleep 1\n\n# Start the Node proxy\nnode /tmp/proxy.js > ~/.openclaw/logs/telephone-http.log 2>&1 &\nsleep 1\n\n# Test\necho \"Health check:\"\ncurl -s http://localhost:8790/health 2>/dev/null\necho \"\"\necho \"Talk test:\"\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:8790/talk -H \"Content-Type: audio/mp4\" --data-binary @/tmp/weather_test.aiff 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1224,"output":248,"cacheRead":69440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70912,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777668796944,"responseId":"064445bdc24719bf3f96ff794e56953a"}}
