{"type":"message","id":"8f2b6d07","parentId":"3640f230","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:53:34.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The proxy is working now. The health check returns 404 because we didn't add a /health route in the proxy, but /talk works. Let me verify the logs and check if the iPhone test will work.\n\nActually, the key thing is that /talk and /messages are being properly proxied to 8791. The iPhone should now be able to use the telephone app through the proxy on port 8790.\n\nLet me also verify Dean is responding properly.\n","thinkingSignature":"a02bf55a37a2c5d17221a6cd2be17efbcdde223db6659851b23e6b35a1663932"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_79o9ft0p6j7n_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sleep 3\necho \"Dean response:\"\ntail -5 ~/.openclaw/logs/telephone-dean.log 2>/dev/null\n\necho \"\"\necho \"HTTP proxy log:\"\ntail -3 ~/.openclaw/logs/telephone-http.log 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":270,"output":175,"cacheRead":70592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71037,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777668810550,"responseId":"064445cb5d59cbc8b3818f8ea39a2661"}}
