{"type":"message","id":"45a23f01","parentId":"786f0788","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:53:48.277Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - all servers are running. The health check is coming back \"Not found\" because the `/talk` GET returns 404 (POST only). But the proxy is working correctly since the POST test returned a proper response.\n\nLet me now tell Bobby to try again. The issue was the Python server wasn't proxying POST requests - now the Node proxy handles it properly.\n","thinkingSignature":"bb12f3a2f5ef1b8887cb596c1aee7a058fca69e5769ae86126ab82f692b82c16"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nFixed! The Python server on port 8790 didn't support POST requests — replaced it with a proper Node proxy that forwards everything to port 8791.\n\n**Try it now:**\n👉 **https://bobbys-macbook-air-1.tail358b13.ts.net/telephone.html**\n\nThe full pipeline should work: tap mic → speak → release → server transcribes → Dean responds → you hear the reply."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":457,"output":162,"cacheRead":71040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71659,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777668823391,"responseId":"064445d748161fd84e842d323fd9800f"}}
