{"type":"message","id":"86700b43","parentId":"f5792752","timestamp":"2026-05-01T22:00:40.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby said he didn't say any of those things. The messages in the JSON show Dean responding to things Bobby never said. This means:\n\n1. Someone else is using the app\n2. Or the app was auto-triggering from tests I ran\n3. Or Bobby tried it and said things but what I saw was from earlier tests\n\nLet me check the logs more carefully to understand what's happening. Bobby said \"I did not say that\" - meaning what he's seeing on the Telephone app doesn't match what he actually said.\n\nThe issue could be:\n1. The transcript isn't matching what he actually said\n2. The responses are coming from wrong transcriptions\n3. There could be duplicate messages or reprocessing\n\nLet me look at what Bobby actually said vs what was transcribed.\n","thinkingSignature":"e04bf83a558184ed56c749a08840cbad3984be76e4e8e409315853734c9dab9b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7mgu8cou3tj4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/logs/telephone-dean.log | tail -30 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":300,"output":201,"cacheRead":94144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94645,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777672834347,"responseId":"0644558284c0e1fd1a7d75fc2e88a0fd"}}
