{"type":"message","id":"08097890","parentId":"0b88a82a","timestamp":"2026-05-01T22:00:56.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the problem now! The last few times the AI connection errored with \"socket hang up\" so Dean fell back to \"I'm here Bobby, say something!\" - but this old response was already in the messages.json from before!\n\nBobby's phone was probably just polling for the reply and picking up these old dean messages that were already there from earlier tests.\n\nAlso I notice Dean is responding with CRAZY wrong dates like \"May 4, 2025\" and \"May 3, 2026\" when asked what time it is - that's weird, the AI should know the current date is May 1, 2026. But that's a separate issue.\n\nThe key issue: Bobby said \"I did not say that\" - meaning he didn't say \"what time is it\" from his phone. The transcript was from my terminal test, not from his iPhone recording. The messages.json has old test messages in it.\n\nLet me clean up and make sure the system is fresh. Also I should fix the TTS issue (ffmpeg errors) that I've been seeing.\n","thinkingSignature":"16fb800247248d22a48adc3413ce48a7472d6c7a325e93c79f0403eaf579c6b5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBobby - those were MY test messages from when I was debugging, not your voice! You didn't say anything.\n\nThe transcript \"What time is it?\" came from me testing from the Mac terminal, not from your iPhone.\n\nLet me clean up and make sure you're getting fresh responses:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rzmmb3xsczz9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Clean slate\npkill -f \"dean.js\" 2>/dev/null; pkill -f \"server.js\" 2>/dev/null\nrm -f ~/Desktop/Telephone/messages.json\nrm -f ~/Desktop/Telephone/.last_check\nsleep 1\n\ncd ~/Desktop/Telephone && node server.js > ~/.openclaw/logs/telephone.log 2>&1 &\nsleep 1\nnode dean.js > ~/.openclaw/logs/telephone-dean.log 2>&1 &\nsleep 2\n\necho \"=== Servers running ===\"\nps aux | grep -E \"server\\.js|dean\\.js\" | grep -v grep | head -3\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Waiting for your voice ===\"\necho \"Try speaking from your iPhone now\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":469,"output":465,"cacheRead":94400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95334,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777672841103,"responseId":"06445589fce0cd3ecd1bfccd2c22151e"}}
