{"type":"message","id":"25d4d6d4","parentId":"9a56658d","timestamp":"2026-05-01T22:53:25.082Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No Dean response in the log for the weather request. The iPhone screenshot showed the transcript saying \"Dean: Hey Bobby! Ready to roll. What's on your mind today?\" and then \"TRY AGAIN\" repeatedly. But there's no weather in the log - it seems the audio transcription is working (Bobby spoke \"what's the weather today\") but the server might not have recorded it.\n\nWait - looking at the transcript in the screenshot it shows \"Dean: Hey Bobby! Ready to roll. What's on your mind today? 🤖🦞\" repeated multiple times. That suggests Bobby tried multiple times and kept getting \"TRY AGAIN\" - the audio isn't playing.\n\nLet me check the server log.\n","thinkingSignature":"ea1f05e141a067897964b371f3ba27c62bc3683b0e3d315a7381562e2b1f27e7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_09fujvmy35m0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -15 ~/.openclaw/logs/telephone.log 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":132,"output":182,"cacheRead":100640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100954,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777676002809,"responseId":"064461e2539a8a775fcbd290042c3df3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c3dd0c77","parentId":"25d4d6d4","timestamp":"2026-05-01T22:53:25.203Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_09fujvmy35m0_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Server] Received 72068 bytes\n[Transcribe] Input file size: 72068 bytes\n[Transcribe] Duration: 1.541315 seconds\n[Transcribe] MP3 size: 8468 bytes\n[Transcribe] Whisper output: /opt/homebrew/Cellar/openai-whisper/20250625_3/libexec/lib/python3.14/site-packages/whisper/transcribe.py:132: UserWarning: FP16 is not supported on CPU; using FP32 instead\n  warnings.warn(\"FP16 is not supported on CPU; using FP32 instead\")\n[00:00.000 --> 00:01.520]  Hello Dean, how are you?\n[Transcribe] Result: Hello Dean, how are you?\n[Server] Transcription: Hello Dean, how are you?\n[Server] Receiving audio, content-type: audio/webm;codecs=opus\n[Server] Received 5 bytes\n[Server] Receiving audio, content-type: audio/webm;codecs=opus\n[Server] Received 5 bytes\n[Server] Receiving audio, content-type: audio/webm;codecs=opus\n[Server] Received 5 bytes"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8,"aggregated":"[Server] Received 72068 bytes\n[Transcribe] Input file size: 72068 bytes\n[Transcribe] Duration: 1.541315 seconds\n[Transcribe] MP3 size: 8468 bytes\n[Transcribe] Whisper output: /opt/homebrew/Cellar/openai-whisper/20250625_3/libexec/lib/python3.14/site-packages/whisper/transcribe.py:132: UserWarning: FP16 is not supported on CPU; using FP32 instead\n  warnings.warn(\"FP16 is not supported on CPU; using FP32 instead\")\n[00:00.000 --> 00:01.520]  Hello Dean, how are you?\n[Transcribe] Result: Hello Dean, how are you?\n[Server] Transcription: Hello Dean, how are you?\n[Server] Receiving audio, content-type: audio/webm;codecs=opus\n[Server] Received 5 bytes\n[Server] Receiving audio, content-type: audio/webm;codecs=opus\n[Server] Received 5 bytes\n[Server] Receiving audio, content-type: audio/webm;codecs=opus\n[Server] Received 5 bytes","cwd":"/