{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"[media attached: /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_249---5200f983-6beb-4a58-83dd-9b87d48a0e47.ogg (audio/ogg; codecs=opus) | /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_249---5200f983-6beb-4a58-83dd-9b87d48a0e47.ogg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Absolute and ~ paths only work when they stay inside your allowed file-read boundary; host file:// URLs are blocked. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n  \"message_id\": \"24217\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"sender\": \"B G\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-05-01 19:22 EDT\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"B G (8212808444)\",\n  \"id\": \"8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"B G\"\n}\n```\n\n<media:audio>","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"16639492","parentId":"bad57df1","timestamp":"2026-05-01T23:22:37.665Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"c0254865","parentId":"16639492","timestamp":"2026-05-01T23:22:43.971Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby sent a voice memo! He wants me to respond with a voice memo too. Let me listen to it first.","thinkingSignature":"98387181147553fe26376e60bcdb7746b19d9c938894b6a019d2577e51eaef8b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ar569p70nri1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Transcribe the voice memo\nffmpeg -i /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_249---5200f983-6beb-4a58-83dd-9b87d48a0e47.ogg /tmp/bobby_voice.mp3 -y 2>/dev/null\nwhisper /tmp/bobby_voice.mp3 --model small.en --language English --output_format txt --output_dir /tmp 2>&1 | grep -v \"UserWarning\\|FP16\\|warnings.warn\" | tail -10\ncat /tmp/bobby_voice.txt 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":101758,"output":181,"cacheRead":224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102163,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777677757665,"responseId":"064468bee901c8dd8a9d30829d8155c1"}}
