not standardized and prone to errors that have security implications. Use the WHATWG URL API instead. CVEs are not issued for `url.parse()` vulnerabilities.\n(Use `node --trace-deprecation ...` to show where the warning was created)","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777677785591}}
{"type":"message","id":"a676badf","parentId":"af91c357","timestamp":"2026-05-01T23:23:09.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The audio proxy is working - it's serving MP3 files. But wait, the issue might be that the `Connection error` is coming from the `/talk` endpoint itself, not the audio. When Bobby holds the mic and releases, the iPhone sends to `/talk` and gets a connection error.\n\nLet me check if the `/talk` endpoint is working. Also, the voice memo Bobby just sent was an OGG file - which means he can record audio. The Telephone app should be doing the same thing.\n\nWait - the voice memo Bobby just sent IS from Telegram. That means Telegram CAN receive voice messages. But the Telephone app is failing. Why?\n\nPossible issues:\n1. The `/talk` endpoint is returning an error when the iPhone sends to it\n\n\n2. The HTTP proxy isn't properly forwarding to the API server on 8791\n3. The iPhone can't reach the Tailscale URL at all\n\nI should check if the proxy is actually running and if the `/talk` endpoint responds correctly.","thinkingSignature":"00131be3cb67316be11bf8004f3d22665307cf6bba70def7b602872f9e4a120e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nGot it Bobby — walkie-talkie style: hold, speak, release, Dean replies. Clear picture.\n\nLet me check one thing about the connection error:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bqwep43kil8h_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test if /talk works\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:8790/talk -H \"Content-Type: audio/webm\" --data-binary @/tmp/hello_dean.aiff 2>/dev/null\necho \"\"\n# Check if proxy is running\nps aux | grep \"proxy.js\" | grep -v grep | head -2"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":555,"output":337,"cacheRead":102336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103228,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777677785595,"responseId":"064468d97d4b