{"type":"message","id":"76dd69f2","parentId":"e1421c35","timestamp":"2026-05-01T23:28:37.230Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The AI call is hanging completely. The gateway is so overloaded that even simple requests are timing out. This is why Dean isn't responding - the AI calls are never completing.\n\nThe gateway is overloaded because:\n1. Event loop delay is 2+ seconds (CPU overloaded)\n2. The gateway itself is consuming massive CPU (53% on the process)\n3. Too many active sessions\n\nLet me wait for the gateway to cool down, or better yet - let me help Bobby with something more important while this is resolved. The gateway overload issue is a system-level problem that's not related to Telephone specifically.\n\nI should let Bobby know the current state and what we're dealing with.\n","thinkingSignature":"178468f781debe0f5b405cf82386785de44a95105d4441c434174558da156339"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBobby — the gateway is **overloaded right now**. That's why Dean isn't responding. The system is so busy that AI calls can't even complete:\n\n```\neventLoopDelayP99Ms=2231ms (2+ second delays!)\nCPU core ratio: 1.165 (overloaded)\n```\n\nThis is why Telephone appears broken. It's not a Telephone problem — the whole OpenClaw system is slammed. I need to wait for it to recover.\n\n**Quick status check:**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eze51xnvfavn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check current load\nps aux | grep \"openclaw/dist/index.js gateway\" | grep -v grep | awk '{print \"CPU: \"$3\"%, MEM: \"$4\"%\"}'\necho \"---\"\n# Count active sessions\nps aux | grep \"node.*openclaw\" | grep -v grep | wc -l\necho \"openclaw processes\"\necho \"---\"\n# Check if we're in a busy heartbeat loop\necho \"Recent errors:\"\ntail -3 ~/.openclaw/logs/gateway.err.log 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":95,"output":364,"cacheRead":106048,"cacheWrite"