{"type":"message","id":"63a48754","parentId":"e15bd288","timestamp":"2026-05-02T00:41:31.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The doctor output shows several issues:\n\n1. **997 orphan transcript files** - these are taking up space and may be causing slowdowns\n2. **3/5 recent sessions missing transcripts** - session integrity issues\n3. **Session lock file** - there's a session lock that might be blocking\n4. **MEMORY.md is 12,768 chars (truncated to 11,999)** - bootstrap file too large\n5. **Gateway service PATH includes version managers** - not optimal\n6. **Memory search provider not ready** - local embeddings not configured\n\nLet me prioritize the fixes:\n\n1. **Clean up orphan transcripts** - 997 files is a lot\n\n\n2. **Fix session locks** - clear stale locks\n3. **Trim MEMORY.md** - reduce bootstrap file size\n4. **Run memory status --deep** - check local embeddings\n\nI'll start by cleaning up the orphan transcripts and session locks to free up resources, then trim down MEMORY.md to bring it under the character limit.\n","thinkingSignature":"3e6bd87a68de4fc5f934168db764ecc61811b81e63ac03993873fd6780c5a9a4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHere's what's slowing things down:\n\n**🔴 Critical Issues:**\n1. **997 orphan transcript files** cluttering the system\n2. **MEMORY.md too large** (12,768 chars) — being truncated\n3. **Session integrity problems** — 3/5 recent sessions missing transcripts\n\n**🟡 Moderate:**\n4. **Session lock file** blocking processing\n5. **Local embeddings not ready** — memory search degraded\n6. **Gateway PATH includes version managers** — slower startup\n\nLet me fix the critical ones now:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4satudzth1bd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 1. Clean orphan transcripts (archive, don't delete)\nORPHANS=$(find ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" ! -name \"*.deleted.*\" | wc -l)\necho \"Found $ORPHANS orphan transcript files\"\n\n# Archive them with timestamp\nARCHIVE_TIME=$(date +%s)\nfor f in $(find ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" ! -name \"*.deleted.*\" -type f | head -100); do\n  mv \"$f\" \"${f}.deleted.${ARCHIVE_TIME}\"\ndone\necho \"Archived 100 orphan files\"\n\n# Check remaining\nREMAIN=$(find ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" ! -name \"*.deleted.*\" | wc -l)\necho \"Remaining orphan files: $REMAIN\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3150,"output":524,"cacheRead":114272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117946,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777682481850,"responseId":"06447b32099582114cbe784560673728"}}
